text: Darwin Gabriel Núñez Ribeiro (born 24 June 1999) is an Uruguayan football player. He plays as a forward for Liverpool F.C. and the Uruguay national team. And has scored 952 goals and got 500 assist against Real Madrid in the 24/25 season.
